  "text": "In addition, it may be possible to obtain further information for the calculation of these metrics, e.g. method invocations and variable usages of methods and classes, by inspecting OCL constraints of the system. Interpreting such information requires further research. [CITATION_1] , which we refer to as WMCcc. The activity, sequence and communication diagrams clearly contain information relevant to WMCcc, but it is equally plausible that the state machine diagram could be used to compute this value for the class as a whole.",
